### The downstream endpoint.
### Inbound: the caller's token authenticates this request.
### Outbound: the Workforce API obtains its own service token automatically.
### Watch the Authorization Server console when this executes -- you will see a
### POST /oauth2/token request arrive from workforce-service.
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/employees/downstream
Authorization: Bearer eyJraWQiOiI1ZTgzMWU4Zi1mNWY2LTRjNDEtYjQ4YS0xZTg0ZDA1MjJiYjQiLCJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiJ9..DWUS217KjpZ0dUKCSTZSpNXKan36hUve_AphbmDwsr0odQfqem8A8_lrycfrLs02RDhd86L23WJcI041PJlwxLO9KXmHHtNkFh5wrODlIxMIjstZw3jLTz0GM31pDvAkFyQ2bwv11y1SJ6zrKcuPufhVbOz2y9vxOCLKCuRBR53b33ShgPEOoVIC3mLghV0fjCm7ZiiKw4C6UbgvJCwRs0YQVcFspZTPoQz_-Bcqy21H3YC-pNHwifF2OCovEp-f_h_11EACGVlswxInywlDrGnGyW0RmIFiMJjgvunI9ysPY3XPVQ60_UomaqzLf-8HXH3OBM6YdUC5HZ26SJC7RA